<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Ortaya Karışık - Terminal</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/" rel="alternate"/><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/feeds/terminal.atom.xml" rel="self"/><id>https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/</id><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><entry><title>Newsboat RSS Feeds Kullanımı</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/newsboat-rss-feeds-kullanimi/" rel="alternate"/><published>2020-07-17T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2020-07-17:/newsboat-rss-feeds-kullanimi/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Terminal tabanlı güçlü bir RSS okuyucu olan Newsboat'u nasıl yapılandıracağınızı ve verimli bir şekilde nasıl kullanacağınızı öğrenin.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Newsboat" class="responsive-img" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, (max-width: 992px) 80vw, (max-width: 1400px) 70vw, 60vw" src="/images/newsboat-xl.webp" srcset="/images/newsboat-sm.webp 300w, /images/newsboat-md.webp 500w, /images/newsboat-xl.webp 800w, /images/newsboat-xl.webp 1200w"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="newsboat-nedir"&gt;Newsboat Nedir? 📰&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newsboat, terminal tabanl&amp;inodot; g&amp;uuml;&amp;ccedil;l&amp;uuml; bir RSS / Atom besleme okuyucusudur. Blog yaz&amp;inodot;lar&amp;inodot;, haberler ve di&amp;gbreve;er i&amp;ccedil;erikleri takip etmek i&amp;ccedil;in idealdir. Unix benzeri sistemlerde &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;r ve esnek yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma se&amp;ccedil;enekleri sunar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="newsboat-kurulumu"&gt;Newsboat Kurulumu 🛠️&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutlarla Newsboat ve ek ara&amp;ccedil;lar&amp;inodot; kurabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;yay&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;newsboat&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;mpv&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;youtube-dl&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;dunst
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mpv&lt;/strong&gt;: Medya oynat&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot; (videolar&amp;inodot; oynatmak i&amp;ccedil;in kullan&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;r).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;youtube-dl&lt;/strong&gt;: RSS i&amp;ccedil;indeki video i&amp;ccedil;eriklerini indirmek i&amp;ccedil;in kullan&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;r.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dunst&lt;/strong&gt;: Masa&amp;uuml;st&amp;uuml; bildirimleri i&amp;ccedil;in (i3-wm kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;lar&amp;inodot; i&amp;ccedil;in gereklidir, di&amp;gbreve;er masa&amp;uuml;st&amp;uuml; ortamlar&amp;inodot; i&amp;ccedil;in zorunlu de&amp;gbreve;ildir).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="yapilandirma"&gt;Yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma 🛠️&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newsboat'un yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma dosyas&amp;inodot; &lt;code&gt;~/.config/newsboat/config&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;ccedil;inde yer al&amp;inodot;r. &amp;Ouml;rnek bir yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rma:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"xdg-open"&lt;/span&gt;

macro&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;o&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"/usr/bin/mpv %u &amp;gt; /dev/null 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1 &amp;amp;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;open-in-browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"xdg-open"&lt;/span&gt;

macro&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;y&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"youtube-dl %u"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;open-in-browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;browser&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"xdg-open"&lt;/span&gt;

