&lt;h2 id="youtube-rss"&gt;YouTube RSS 📺&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Abone oldu&amp;gbreve;unuz YouTube kanallar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; Newsboat'a eklemek i&amp;ccedil;in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/subscription_manager" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;YouTube Abonelikler Sayfas&amp;inodot;&lt;/a&gt;'na gidin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;"RSS okuyuculara d&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;a aktar" se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;iyle dosyan&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; indirin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutla RSS adreslerini i&amp;ccedil;eri aktar&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
